Package: qfwr
Type: Package
Title: Tools for "Quantitative Finance with R" course
Version: 0.0.6
Author: Yongyi Zeng
Maintainer: Yongyi Zeng <zzyy@xmu.edu.cn>
Description: Tools for my course "Quantitative Finance with R" (QFwR)
    to facilitate teaching and learning. The interactive exercise is
    mainly powered by RStudio's `learnr`, DataCamp's `testwhat` package 
    and Rundel's `learnrhash`.
